<main>
  <h2>About Uplift Digital</h2>

  <p>Uplift Digital was founded with a simple but powerful goal: to make mental health support accessible to everyone, everywhere. We understand that mental wellness is a journey — and we're here to walk that path with you.</p>

  <h3>Our Story</h3>
  <p>Born from a passion for mental health advocacy, Uplift Digital brings together licensed professionals, supportive communities, and reliable resources all in one digital space. We believe that no one should ever feel alone when facing mental health challenges.</p>

  <h3>What We Stand For</h3>
  <ul class="about-list">
    <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Mental health resources should be available to all, no matter where you are.</li>
    <li><strong>Community:</strong> Healing is stronger when shared with others who understand and support you.</li>
    <li><strong>Empowerment:</strong> We aim to equip individuals with tools and knowledge to take control of their mental health journey.</li>
    <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> We respect your privacy and provide safe, secure ways to seek help and support.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Meet Our Team</h3>
  <p>Our network includes experienced therapists, counselors, peer supporters, and mental health advocates — all united by a shared mission to uplift others.</p>

  <p><strong>At Uplift Digital, you are never alone. Your journey matters. Your story matters.</strong></p>

</main>

